♪Only to keep the moon in sight♪

213
00:16:08,890 --> 00:16:12,330
♪For it once shone upon your face♪

214
00:16:13,090 --> 00:16:16,290
♪When you looked at me in the eye♪

215
00:16:17,050 --> 00:16:20,050
♪I've said goodbye a thousand times♪

216
00:16:20,050 --> 00:16:23,930
♪Only to call your name again♪

217
00:16:24,330 --> 00:16:28,010
♪For it's the only thing♪

218
00:16:28,290 --> 00:16:32,010
♪I'll never forget♪

