♪I've said goodbye a thousand times♪

224
00:16:51,050 --> 00:16:55,010
♪Only to call your name again♪

225
00:16:55,330 --> 00:16:58,690
♪For it's the only thing♪

226
00:16:59,210 --> 00:17:03,010
♪I'll never forget♪

227
00:17:06,890 --> 00:17:10,250
♪Till the day that I die♪
